            <p class="text-2xl text-slate-700 font-medium">
                Millions of seniors live without primary caretakers. Current healthcare is reactive—treating issues only after they become emergencies. 
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-slate-100">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            <div>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-teal-800 mb-6">Our Solution</h2>
                <ul class="space-y-6 text-xl">
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <span class="text-teal-600 mr-3 text-2xl">✔</span>
                        <span><strong>Early Diagnosis:</strong> Continuous monitoring that flags complications early.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <span class="text-teal-600 mr-3 text-2xl">✔</span>
                        <span><strong>Senior-First UX:</strong> High-contrast, voice-enabled, and zero-friction interface.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <span class="text-teal-600 mr-3 text-2xl">✔</span>
                        <span><strong>Independence:</strong> Tools designed for users without live-in assistance.</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-teal-700 h-64 rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center text-white text-xl font-bold shadow-lg">
                [Product Demo Visual Here]
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact" class="py-24 px-6 text-center bg-teal-900 text-white">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to Transform Senior Healthcare?</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-teal-100 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Join us in building the future of preventive aging. View our full financial projections and roadmap.
        </p>
        <button class="bg-white text-teal-900 text-xl font-bold py-4 px-12 rounded-full hover:bg-teal-50 transition transform hover:scale-105">
            Contact for Investment
        </button>
    </section>

    <footer class="py-10 text-center text-slate-500 border-t border-slate-200">
        <p>&copy; 2026 SeniorCare AI. Built with Vibe Coding.</p>
    </footer>

